{"generated": "2026-07-20 16:05", "curation": {"market": "개인 투자자 여러분, 안녕하십니까. 지난 24시간 동안 시장은 여러 복합적인 요인으로 인해 큰 변동성을 보였습니다. 핵심 테마를 중심으로 시장 상황을 브리핑해 드립니다.\n\n<b>1. 코스피 급락과 6,500선 방어</b>\n코스피는 미국 증시의 약세와 반도체 관련 악재가 겹치며 4.46% 급락, 6,500선 턱걸이 마감했습니다. 특히 '검은 월요일'로 불리며 2거래일 연속 매도 사이드카가 발동되었고, 개인 투자자들의 손실이 컸습니다. [<a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiT0FVX3lxTE1Rd20yb3NrWTNSbHlNNnNUMmRyZDh5UjNGcVlMemcyRHVabHZuNEdpVnpWLU1YZkEtV082b1ZPVzgzOVphVGNIS2NCVEx1dXc?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#1</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMicEFVX3lxTFA4VWVyS2N5VEdkVmlDV1d2TWFfeUtJc3o5dUJCRVVRY2d1TDFmdVN2aTZsV2tjeGZ5SzZ0cVdsYkJwVWJHZ2VzU2JzUXc4QzhRUlFIZFliNmZkVnA5Um9pdG1kRXpwLWZXeU9vbC11ejI?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#2</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiUkFVX3lxTE1tNGtabXRmbnpuM1o4ZDNYaHlyYkFaY2xHNi11ME1saEJvWHNwamh6ZWNGNkNkT0xvR0NVLUNKblNoSEtHcVF4amR1SFVuemdGcmc?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#4</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiXkFVX3lxTE0zYUNFeGJ1eDY0N05SZ2VJbTJYd0RocGY1eF8wRVhtNHhIYW1tSVBsWnEzWV9BMFJuOHBhZzBfQlJaU01KY0VkNXRSRlFuNkVNMzM5d2ZZVWhYbkVQRFE?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#5</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#7</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiXkFVX3lxTE10cW5WMTRZM0kyc1ZMdFZ4SGFmblhEN1BhMVJGaElQaHZJYUdLdm81cW5ZNlRUUC1JYlRLRVlzVktGNmZiY2tUN0ZjRlNsR0FvMXBpcHhiMmwxNG9pREE?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#16</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiUEFVX3lxTE1ra1lvclpvQzV6WExOYkZEb1M2aTBlWWtZWkNZZ0VpZE5ZNE85aFhUeEZNZFd1RUVhR3p1WXM1NXhmMFM2VFBqeVVzbDluZWw1?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#25</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiXkFVX3lxTE9BRXc0VWxKOG9aY0lHY1U2TzdDNll5bWYxZTBnX05XdEJidGlJVmZMYy1QeE5xY1Q0andMQ2xZM0h2M09US3Bnb1BUNnlDN2cyR25acFpOSFRMMTJuZEE?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#27</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMickFVX3lxTE9ONmx4blF0bEFET1lBTWdNLVk3QW5yRUJLd2lkRWxTSjZnbk8tLXp3T3dxcmpPempINlFfeEROb0JneHh4UG1JRll4UFJQZkRDRk9fR3V1VWdUTDNNaGdheVJSS1hTdFBfcHhJS2VHTlpRdw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#29</a>]\n\n<b>2. 반도체 산업의 엇갈린 전망</b>\n반도체 산업은 시장의 가장 큰 화두였습니다. 한편으로는 AI 호황에 힘입어 신입 채용 공고가 상반기에 47% 급증하고, 한국 1인당 GDP 4만 달러 시대 진입을 견인할 것이라는 긍정적인 전망이 있었습니다. 그러나 다른 한편으로는 '반도체 피크아웃' 우려와 함께 삼성전자, SK하이닉스 등 주요 반도체 기업 주가가 4% 하락하며 시장 급락을 주도했습니다. 일부 전문가들은 반도체 피크아웃 우려가 과도하며, 6,000선대가 비중 확대의 기회라고 분석했습니다. 또한, 한국은행은 반도체 쏠림 심화에 따른 '네덜란드병' 가능성을 경고했습니다. [<a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiXkFVX3lxTE0zYUNFeGJ1eDY0N05SZ2VJbTJYd0RocGY1eF8wRVhtNHhIYW1tSVBsWnEzWV9BMFJuOHBhZzBfQlJaU01KY0VkNXRSRlFuNkVNMzM5d2ZZVWhYbkVQRFE?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#5</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMibEFVX3lxTE1rU2liLU5ldW5qUkw2NHpINnFhYnVJMzBsNXZBMG1nOTd2X0FZTnFubUNxTTcxTEVBMUZJMVcxMFBnQzJ2SUZkcWMzNEJEeUc0c1VZeVphU19fd1NyZ2xUVm1qdm1mQl9qcm4zOQ?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#6</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#9</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiY0FVX3lxTFBSdE93VHFwNmIxQ2Q2MDNNaFRXcEl1eDZwc19IcEhPbnhiUW9Bc3hmbEZrQ1BTMUstel95TzJLZ0w5VUNfRGVVN25CeEtyYTJMMXF1OVBXTDdXOVVPTmhlVnV6Yw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#12</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiZ0FVX3lxTE91X3dhNmhxd1RrSW5jVDJSRWFydUlPNmY0YW5HTEJKUE9tRXNBLXV2aGJSZ0stLUd0QVlfb2pHUmh2T0QtbzBXV0F2LUdfeTE2TWRxTU5TdHZmalJYWExDaFM4b2tiZTg?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#13</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMickFVX3lxTE42Z2hUWjZfdzY0V0F0eVFLSFBSRjg4cV9HZDFDbHpNTl9oSWZzdEdtX0VySGtRNjF4dVZnNDlGaWdmaHp3c2JRZXJLV0FvMUZXNFZRenhZRmwyX3VJaFpQZks1cTdNSEk5UDVMQnpld2VMZw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#15</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiaEFVX3lxTFA1ZlZKUGlsRmpPQTdlRU1LQXoxVlN3MnZwdm1vRGZWSWwyZExXV3RhdEhpTG96bE5jM3dHVUtfbnJLV2FyTlJTWHByUEV0OTJNbC1TNlJFSkV